import React, { useState } from 'react' import axios from 'axios'; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; const Register = () => { const [name, setName ] = useState(''); const [email, setEmail ] = useState(''); const [password, setPassword ] = useState(''); const [confPassword, setConfPassword ] = useState(''); const navigate = useNavigate(); const Register = async(e) => { e.preventDefault(); try { await axios.post('http://localhost:5000/users', { name: name, email: email, password: password, confPassword : confPassword }); navigate.push("/"); } catch (error) { console.log(error) } } return (
Name
setName(e.target.value)}/>

setEmail(e.target.value)}/>

setPassword(e.target.value)}/>

setConfPassword(e.target.value)}/>
) } export default Register
